        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/chord-browser-metronome.png" alt="Chord Browser & Metronome" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Chord Browser & Metronome</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Browse chords and practice with the built-in metronome for perfect timing.</p></div></div>
            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/chord-filter.png" alt="Chord Filter" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Instant Chord Charts</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Instant chord charts and filtering for any detected chord.</p></div></div>
            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/circle-guitar-chords-light.png" alt="Circle of Fifths" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Circle of Fifths</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Circle of Fifths with real-time chord detection and key visualization.</p></div></div>
