            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/key-lock.png" alt="Key Lock" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Key Lock</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Lock in your key and stay in tune throughout your session.</p></div></div>
            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/logo-circle-next-chords.png" alt="Next Chords" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Next Chord Predictions</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Next chord predictions keep you ahead of the progression.</p></div></div>
            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/metronome-strum-patterns.png" alt="Metronome & Strum Patterns" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Metronome & Strum Patterns</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Practice strum patterns and rhythms with the metronome.</p></div></div>
            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/tablet_full_screen_lyrics.png" alt="Full Screen Lyrics" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Full Screen Lyrics</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Full-screen lyrics display for easy reading while you play.</p></div></div>
            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/tablet_lyrics_and_recording.png" alt="Lyrics & Recording" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Lyrics & Recording</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Record your performance while following along with lyrics.</p></div></div>
            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/tuner.png" alt="Tuner" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Chromatic Tuner</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Chromatic tuner for precise instrument tuning.</p></div></div>
