            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/tunes-sheet-audio.png" alt="Sheet Music & Audio" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Sheet Music & Audio</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Record audio and attach sheet music to your compositions.</p></div></div>
