            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/uke-dark.png" alt="Ukulele Support" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Ukulele Support</h4><p class="text-gray-300">Support for guitar, bass, ukulele, baratone ukulele and mandolin, so far.</p></div></div>
            <div class="carousel-slide"><div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mx-2"><div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-10 mb-4"><img src="/images/features/watch-circle.png" alt="Watch Circle" class="object-contain bg-gray-700 rounded" /></div><h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Watch Circle</h4><p class="text-gray-300">(Coming soon) Circle of Fifths visualization on your smartwatch.</p></div></div>
