    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-blue-100 to-purple-100 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Ready to Jam Smarter?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Grab JamBuddy and start seeing chords in real time on your favorite instruments.
      </p>
